Build instructions
1) ./configure --with-apache=/path/to/apache
2) make
3) su -c "make install"

a sample config entry

Listen 21
<VirtualHost *:21>
   FTPprotocol on
<directory /tmp/pop>
   AuthDBMUserFile /usr/local/httpd/pop3
   AuthName pop3
   AuthType Basic
   require valid-user
</directory>
</VirtualHost>
